net.sourceforge.seqware.common.hibernate
Class FindAllTheFiles

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.seqware.common.hibernate.FindAllTheFiles

public class FindAllTheFiles
extends Object

Should only be used for one query and then discarded and re-instantiated. The Session needs to be open for it to work (InSessionExecution). The list of files is returned as-is, so I make no guarantees on constancy.
